quran[4]{c,v,t}:
  16,22,"Your God is One God. As for those who do not have iman in the Next World, their hearts are in denial and they are puffed up with pride"
  16,23,There is no doubt that Allah knows what they keep secret and what they make public. He does not love people puffed up with pride
  16,24,"When they are asked, ´What has your Lord sent down?´ they say, ´Myths and legends of previous peoples.´"
  16,25,So on the Day of Rising they will carry the full weight of their own burdens and some of the burdens of those they misguided without knowledge. What an evil load they bear